description:
This video is brought to you by Nebula Originals. Get a GREAT deal on Nebula now: https://go.nebula.tv/captainmidnight
In 1994, Burt Reynolds went on Jay Leno and things got weird very quickly, in this very strange chapter of talk show history. When Nickelodeon host Marc Summers made a few jokes at his expense, Burt lost it. This is my commentary on that incident.
